    "These tools can harness real-time data from multiple sources to provide accurate, near-instantaneous assessments of the grid's status.",
    "Such models could not only forecast potential threats but also suggest optimal reactive measures in real time, enhancing the adaptability and robustness of the system.",
    "Moreover, the development of distributed energy resources such as solar plants, wind plants, and battery storage systems, provides an opportunity to create localized emergency control strategies.",
    "By allowing areas of the grid to function independently during crises, these resources can help mitigate the risk of widespread blackouts.",
